name: NeoFiend Wings of Revontheus
description: Fiends, much like hawks, rip flesh and tear should apart. Fight for the glory of your Commander, members of the Nulgath Nation! Given to the Nation early as a reward from the ArcFiend for winning the second skirmish of the Dage vs Nulgath war! (Six Diamonds required. 1 for each of Nulgath's all-seeing eyes.)
